                     <interp inst="t18280529-97-off530" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280529-97-cd531" type="crimeDate">22d of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-97-off530 t18280529-97-cd531"></join>, 1 pair of boots, value 2s. 6d., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18280529-97-victim614" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Sampson the elder<interp inst="t18280529-97-victim614" type="surname" value="Sampson"></interp>
